Package: reducedscan
Title: QTL Scans with Simpler Statistical Models in Multiparental Populations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Frederick",
           family = "Boehm",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "frederick.boehm@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1644-5931"))
Description: We infer allelic series (number of alleles and mapping from 
    founder lines to alleles, ie, which founders share alleles) and perform 
    QTL scans with corresponding 'reduced' statistical models with one 
    allele effect parameter per inferred allele.
